Split a data frame into a list of subsets by variables

split-by.Rd

Split a data frame into a list of subsets by variables

split_by(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A data frame.
...

A list of unquoted variables, separated by commas, to split a dataset.

Examples

pedestrian %>%
  split_by(Sensor)
